{"tid":417960,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本網站調查《今昔對比漂亮的女藝人》","createTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T19:53:59.000Z","uid":60286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"54d68d74b3f83e498f0ecc2380b634ebec2bee1d","tid":417960,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/143746_daa30f6fb3d115f4524aac03d0fd29b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F143746_daa30f6fb3d115f4524aac03d0fd29b0.jpg&h=27a768a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女明星最常被拿出來比較的東西是什麼，拍攝的作品或是出席某個重要場合的服裝？想想其實出道當時跟現今的對比也是常常被拿出來討論的一點，日前日本網站「R25」就對日本年輕男性做了一份調查，那麼倒底有誰剛開始時最青澀，又是誰現今變化最大，變成大家印象中超漂亮的美女呢？<br />\n<br />\n第十名　波瑠<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144030_303d630c8ebd88cd807cd5d7e2f81761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144030_303d630c8ebd88cd807cd5d7e2f81761.jpg&h=14a12817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n91年生的波瑠，長頭髮時期看起來就是小女生一枚，雖然出演過當時紅極一時的《戀空》，但是也沒有給人留下太多的印象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144223_c18ee0f19e8db87bb1559d7b2dc8fc37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144223_c18ee0f19e8db87bb1559d7b2dc8fc37.jpg&h=8df1faa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第九名　多部未華子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144250_5a055f2b2b03073b30f2a473f2ea376e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144250_5a055f2b2b03073b30f2a473f2ea376e.jpg&h=e35309f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾因主演電影《我愛奇諾奧》及《青空下講我知你愛我》而獲得關注，獲得日本電影藍絲帶獎最佳新人獎 。那時候看起來超級青澀單純的！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144315_9c7f3384b23a4e927d969c84fc36674d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144315_9c7f3384b23a4e927d969c84fc36674d.jpg&h=15bedbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越來越成熟的多部未華子星路似乎是一帆風順，娃娃臉的長相也給觀眾們留下了非常深刻的印象，妹子真的是越來越好看了呢！<br />\n<br />\n第八名　佐佐木希<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144349_f3c7f40dbd889c41d7c42fcaac93ea5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144349_f3c7f40dbd889c41d7c42fcaac93ea5a.jpg&h=555e52e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n88年的佐佐木希，被日本漫畫雜誌舉辦的「日本全國尋找美女」活動的搜查員發掘，正式出道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144658_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144658_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg&h=b264c32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出演過非常多電影和電視劇之後的佐佐木希，演技更加精湛了，而且在妝容和穿著方面也越來越好，絕對是女神級別的存在了<br />\n<br />\n第七名　上戸彩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144749_473800e8faf58ff775eceec9941f3ea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144749_473800e8faf58ff775eceec9941f3ea7.jpg&h=0ed81b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n85年的上戸彩，2004年憑藉《網球甜心》獲得第40屆日劇學院賞最佳女主角獎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/144940_9d4ee339efed37598a3f8b9fd2cc0177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F144940_9d4ee339efed37598a3f8b9fd2cc0177.jpg&h=214844b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為本身長相就非常甜美，2005年，上戶彩獲得最佳髮型獎、最佳笑容獎及美甲皇后。2007年年僅20歲的上戶彩在日本偶像雜誌《Junon》「心目中五官最漂亮的女星」評選活動中排在了第三位。<br />\n<br />\n第六名　綾瀬遙<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145010_561a8cf732ab1b90f888ad064d13b1ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145010_561a8cf732ab1b90f888ad064d13b1ab.jpg&h=342a83dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2004年，綾瀨遙參與拍攝電視劇《在世界中心呼喚愛》，憑藉這部影片獲得第42屆日劇學院賞最佳女配角獎 。2007年，主演《螢之光》獲日劇GP大賞最佳女主角獎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145056_4fb6940c645748a45603bb4099386f71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145056_4fb6940c645748a45603bb4099386f71.jpg&h=bb2ba3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145112_a7306ce374570295614f6f9b12bab2a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145112_a7306ce374570295614f6f9b12bab2a7.jpg&h=97eec450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一出道起點就非常高的綾瀨遙，在2016年3月14日，更是奪得日媒票選「最理想女友」冠軍，成功連續三年稱霸，更是該排行榜舉辦9屆以來第5度奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n第五名　新垣結衣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145140_681c9354f2c50d31f2a4e1aedaa3f790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145140_681c9354f2c50d31f2a4e1aedaa3f790.jpg&h=4b7aebbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n88年的新垣結衣，2001年Gakki參加《nicola》模特比賽並獲得最優秀獎。2005年參與拍攝《龍櫻》讓人們對這個笑容甜美的女孩子留下了深刻的印象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145335_afefcb72eaa08ac92cc77a5ef8c70f6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145335_afefcb72eaa08ac92cc77a5ef8c70f6a.jpg&h=dde90d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145249_ba1d21996dcce101cadda5ab7bfe8041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145249_ba1d21996dcce101cadda5ab7bfe8041.jpg&h=c7ba1dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2007年，Gakki主演電影《戀空》而知名度增加，並接連獲得多個電影新人獎項。因為純真的笑容和甜美的長相，Gakki被人們稱為「治癒系」美少女。<br />\n<br />\n第四名　井上真央<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145404_4e5b91fc9b42e90a00b15c64a8ff63af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145404_4e5b91fc9b42e90a00b15c64a8ff63af.jpg&h=524b6b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n87年的井上真央，1992年的時候童星出道，1995年出演NHK電視劇《藏》，演技獲得肯定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145532_8fb473e9b3b699194f94cf7ea7409dbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145532_8fb473e9b3b699194f94cf7ea7409dbb.jpg&h=7fcabe26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2011年，井上真央主演NHK晨間劇《太陽公公》平均收視率18.8%，也因此被選為第62屆《紅白歌會》紅組司儀，並帶領紅組取得勝利，終結六連敗 。"},{"pid":"a8cb7f16e7dc4a9204ca90f9c37f1e8110668f6a","tid":417960,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"第三名　堀北真希<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145606_9fd6f87c215baacecbbcee007b7365b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145606_9fd6f87c215baacecbbcee007b7365b8.jpg&h=164110ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本網友對於堀北真希的印象，有很多都是都停留在野豬妹的那個時候，覺得當時的她有點酷酷又帶有一點老土的感覺，但現在一看不但跟當時的印象差距很多，而且變得超有女人味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145729_dc2f7ef2fb7d3bb5decde772c90495c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145729_dc2f7ef2fb7d3bb5decde772c90495c9.jpg&h=8f7dd2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被譽為日本國民女星的堀北真希，從2003年出道之後就一直活躍在演藝一線，雖然今年3月1日已經宣布退出演藝圈回歸家庭，還是希望女神有一天能重回演藝圈吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145832_e38127f1a151374587ad526c18745fe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145832_e38127f1a151374587ad526c18745fe1.jpg&h=5724eac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二名　深田恭子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145906_f14a26c24423432bfbfeec49d0d52ee4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145906_f14a26c24423432bfbfeec49d0d52ee4.jpg&h=75ad13f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剛出道的深田恭子就因為嬰兒肥而讓人覺得超級可愛的，不過總給人一種不是很成熟的感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/145930_7fbb44fab5b04337eb7cb4b273d5c0f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F145930_7fbb44fab5b04337eb7cb4b273d5c0f1.jpg&h=e0a1c65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/150018_49f033fa84ef926525f26442848d1eba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F150018_49f033fa84ef926525f26442848d1eba.jpg&h=fd0a15d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而現在的深田恭子，不但有著跟年齡相符的成熟感，外貌和性感都已經變得非常脫俗的感覺了~<br />\n<br />\n第一名　石原里美<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/150045_cac52a513fbe6bb0beaaf8353d2944af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F150045_cac52a513fbe6bb0beaaf8353d2944af.jpg&h=c9c9a5c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許多網友回顧早些年她拍戲時的模樣，都跟現在搭不太起來，是最有感判若兩人的日本當紅女星<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/150103_ffd9bbca7977daa05637963982d127e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F150103_ffd9bbca7977daa05637963982d127e6.jpg&h=02e15c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/150227_4dcf262d0d5565b12bc4b04ca8b264ef.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F150227_4dcf262d0d5565b12bc4b04ca8b264ef.jpeg&h=250edf6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abff7b97b731d6395182e24ecb5cc0a28eef612c","tid":417960,"uid":26266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"佐佐木希舊時張相好mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b91905cfe73abfb148b53deea63a76cf9284f9e","tid":417960,"uid":62555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"以為有朱千雪"},{"pid":"6bbdd0d1560f0d6970c4312ffc0bec5da65542ca","tid":417960,"uid":119102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佐佐木希舊時張相好mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家師奶"},{"pid":"a63f407c855f57129338fde3fd103429db39878d","tid":417960,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"一路碌落去一路諗,<br />\n<br />\n千雪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b33826e8fb993a1b800b66a12a96378e6d2fc","tid":417960,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"戶田呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05235e0dd1041e827848ceea3d2fdcb1ae5d314","tid":417960,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"恭子直情變咗另一個人，認唔到"},{"pid":"4759f57fdd1d7e5a5d0f0b91628e35ffc11bf64f","tid":417960,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"石原里美 最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe5cf8e54651aeb30529a5d40f0265b93fbe370","tid":417960,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"石原明明一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f01357e63b2cde3319c6c03ce239e1368128a2","tid":417960,"uid":6794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"石原根本以前仲正"},{"pid":"b754e377fe742e3da1d73d1f5c54199380220876","tid":417960,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:24:08.000Z","msg":"如果ZARD仲在生<br />\n除左結衣 石原 全部秒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd5a281494cf918fc3252616893033c7dc74358","tid":417960,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"肥恭整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce7027d19fee8a4407c8e3149246b6d88f44a12","tid":417960,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果ZARD仲在生<br />\n除左結衣 石原 全部秒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80b182e6975970d1ef10b9770728248a0f10571","tid":417960,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔知點解 見到呢類標題 總會覺得第一會係朱千雪"},{"pid":"b9bcbc8c1c2054d2fb67c7e0e092363a13ed6cbc","tid":417960,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果ZARD仲在生<br />\n除左結衣 石原 全部秒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結衣都唔係好頂得住，泉水啲氣質真係好勁。"},{"pid":"52cc27689522e3f7e92c2499198fb03d522e99fb","tid":417960,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T19:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>石原明明一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}